cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY. 

The paper discusses Federated Learning, which is a machine learning setting, and proposes two methods to reduce the uplink communication costs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as the paper deals with distributed learning. The paper also experiments on convolutional and recurrent networks, indicating that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper proposes methods to improve communication efficiency, which could also place it in the cs.SY (Systems and Control) category.
